      "description": "Subjects PLDC to laws regarding land exchanges, land use, zoning, and OHA's pro rata portion of the public land trust. Requires PLDC to consult with OHA. Increases membership of the board of directors of PLDC from 5 to 7. Requires the Hawaii public land optimization plan to include the protection of cultural practices. Requires PLDC to include a culturally-sensitive development plan for each of its projects."
