      "description": "Establishes the maternal mortality review panel to conduct comprehensive reviews of maternal deaths in Hawaii that includes collecting, analyzing, and disseminating maternal mortality information. Requires the committee to hold meetings and submit an annual report to the legislature. Makes appropriation. Effective July 1, 2050. (SB1238 HD1)"
