      "last_action": "The committee(s) on EEP recommend(s) that the measure be deferred.",
      "title": "Invasive Species; Pests; Inspections, Treatment, and Destruction; Transport; Prohibitions; Quarantine; Penalties",
      "description": "Makes regulated articles subject to pest inspection, treatment, and destruction. Prohibits transportation of designated pests or diseased or infested articles. Prohibits possession, harboring, transportation, rearing, breeding, distribution, or release of pests except as allowed by permit. Allows designation of quarantine areas and establishment of compliance agreements for transportation of certain articles. Establishes penalties for violations. Effective 7\/1\/2050. (HD1)"
